      <title>Nuveen 的 Rodriguez 预计收益率曲线将在 2025 年趋陡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/nuveen-s-rodriguez-expects-yield-curve-to-steepen-in-25-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nuveen 固定收益策略主管 Tony Rodriguez 预计收益率曲线将在 2025 年变陡。他还预计今年通胀率将缓慢下降。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/nuveen-s-rodriguez-expects-yield-curve-to-steepen-in-25-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
